    <objectives>
      <material>
        <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;h1&gt;Session 5 Quiz – Objects and Object Methods&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Test your understanding of object literals, properties, methods, and object manipulation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Topics Covered:&lt;/strong&gt;
- Object creation and access
- Dot vs bracket notation
- Object methods
- this keyword
- Object destructuring
- Object.keys, Object.values, Object.entries&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions:&lt;/strong&gt;
- 16 questions from the Session 5 question bank
- 20 minute time limit
- 3 attempts allowed
- 16 points total (1 point per question)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;After syncing the question bank to Canvas:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</mattext>
      </material>
    </objectives>
